{"tid":624002,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 JJ 三揀二( NIER,龍珠FIGHTER,ODIN)","createTime":"2018-04-10T12:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T13:36:37.000Z","uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"42b14a34edd4ed4828cf75f1bd7778f639f1b638","tid":624002,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"放假想搵啲GAME煲下,呢三隻睇過評價都好好<br />\n<br />\n1. NIER- 講深度劇情,仲係2017 神作<br />\n2. 龍珠 - 其實本人唔太好格鬥GAME,但係龍珠太有回憶,呢隻又整得好<br />\n3. ODIN SPHERE- 聽講又係2D神作,故事又好好<br />\n<br />\n俾你地揀二隻會點揀? 我暫時心思思係1,2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a3182791b83fe2bc48968f0bb7fd21a8466d53","tid":624002,"uid":46390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"隻龍珠個故事mode做得好差，但格鬥做得好好<br />\n應該當佢係街霸、拳皇個類格鬥game<br />\n<br />\n不過格鬥game黎講係最易上手，可以試下玩"},{"pid":"2be89cc40b7b91da74143262297933750280babf","tid":624002,"uid":82815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"Nier啦 起嘛玩幾十個鐘"},{"pid":"8d2ef4bb25e682b5d4c8311e7bd0caf8ed88949d","tid":624002,"uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be89cc40b7b91da74143262297933750280babf","tid":624002,"uid":82815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"Nier啦 起嘛玩幾十個鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"呢隻基本上必入玩過試玩都覺得唔簡單<br />\n<br />\n不過係咪入普通版就夠？豪華版好似都無咩特別。"},{"pid":"7c58caa8db30f73f9cd390c5840bee188f3035c5","tid":624002,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d2ef4bb25e682b5d4c8311e7bd0caf8ed88949d","tid":624002,"uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be89cc40b7b91da74143262297933750280babf","tid":624002,"uid":82815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:51:45.000Z","msg"